  <name>Flow</name>
  <summary>A modern privacy-focused browser with a minimalistic design</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Flow is a modern, privacy-focused web browser built on Chromium with a clean,
      minimalistic design. It aims to provide a fast, secure, and intuitive browsing
      experience while respecting user privacy.
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Privacy-focused browsing with built-in protections</li>
      <li>Clean, minimalistic user interface</li>
      <li>Support for Chrome extensions</li>
      <li>Multiple profile support</li>
      <li>Wayland and X11 support</li>
      <li>PDF viewing</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">dev.iamevan.flow.desktop</launchable>

  <url type="homepage">https://github.com/MultiboxLabs/flow-browser</url>
